{"tid":1467091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你話今日失民意 我話其實係軍心","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:09:17.000Z","uid":193415,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6eab0bbbf840793b4495e83aec277c123c458dbd","tid":1467091,"uid":193415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:28.000Z","msg":"唔好屌我P牌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />少開post 唔啱聽由佢沉<br />\n<br />\n好多人話今日失左民意 但我覺得係軍心<br />\n係嘅有啲遊客覺得我地搞到佢<br />\n身邊都有人覺得今日做錯要改善下<br />\n民意冇失過 因為同路人就算唔認同都會理解<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日最大問題係大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">軍心不穩</span></span></strong><br />\n一嚟今日好多鬼引我地入局<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n二嚟今日行動上未有共識，例如比/唔比遊客過<br />\n搞到好多現場手足都覺得無力感好大 或者好嬲<br />\n<br />\n其實過多排睇返<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">今日只係好小事</span></span></strong><br />\n做得未夠好咪理性討論下點樣再做好啲囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由69到依家都係咁 因為<span style=\"color: orange;\">冇大台</span>先會咁多分歧<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">懇請不要被仇恨支配自己</span></strong></span><br />\n重整軍心 重新出發<br />\n<br />\n唔好質疑自己 唔好質疑同路人<br />\n就算同你意見相反 大家都係想個結果好<br />\n唔好喺哩個時候先互相對罵質疑<br />\n<br />\n各位手足 <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>齊上齊落 永不割𥱊</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"55bc58b5bc95c74f86d424147b9b49c466335cf5","tid":1467091,"uid":193415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:06:33.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"92dc9c07719377feb649c990c974c153af22e929","tid":1467091,"uid":193415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:06:43.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"b1a3b19d3d930f6753fa1536e7fabfa0304efb4f","tid":1467091,"uid":193415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:06:56.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"11596bbfc773b079a2d11c18f5727d864b118b2f","tid":1467091,"uid":193415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:07:14.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"9bc2ebb58b3bd00563d114376996678cdec943a1","tid":1467091,"uid":193415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:08:11.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"83cc2a445ad79f1d4135e164c9a15a5ddf0616e0","tid":1467091,"uid":193415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:08:27.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"803619a3230fc7046b0d703186ca636cefdc3baf","tid":1467091,"uid":193415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:08:38.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"1887786ccb25e6a7a2909d376b974cb93d085330","tid":1467091,"uid":193415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:08:48.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"2cff191aa0c3bd3a02a46682e139b90140bffa09","tid":1467091,"uid":193415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:09:07.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"74e57b5822edd8aa7afb0d8e5dda9b20d8fbd576","tid":1467091,"uid":193415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:09:17.000Z","msg":"10/10"}]}